Reserves and Academy|Liverpool]] | years1 = 2018- | clubs1 = [[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]] | caps1 = 0 | goals1 = 0 | club-update = 16:56, 23 August 2018 (UTC) }} '''Nathaniel Phillips''' (born 21 March 1997), is an English professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]], as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espnfc.com/player/275109/nathaniel-phillips |title=Nathaniel Phillips |publisher=ESPN FC |website=espnfc.com |access-date=2018-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181026222938/http://www.espnfc.com/player/275109/nathaniel-phillips# |archive-date=2018-10-26 |dead-url=no |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2019/clubs/player=150515920/index.html |title=Nathaniel Phillips |publisher=UEFA |website=uefa.com |access-date=2018-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181026232521/https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2019/clubs/player=150515920/index.html# |archive-date=2018-10-26 |dead-url=no |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.premierleague.com/players/14051/Nathaniel-Phillips/overview |title=Nathaniel Phillips |publisher=Premier League |website=premierleague.com |access-date=2018-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181027021634/https://www.premierleague.com/players/14051/Nathaniel-Phillips/overview# |archive-date=2018-10-27 |dead-url=no |df= }}</ref>
==Career== Phillips joined Liverpool ahead of the [[2016–17 Liverpool F.C. season|2016–17 season]] on a free transfer from [[Bolton Wanderers F.C.|Bolton Wanderers]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.liverpoolfc.com/team/first-team/player/nathaniel-phillips|title=Profile|accessdate=23 August 2018|publisher=Liverpool F.C.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806162625/https://www.liverpoolfc.com/team/first-team/player/nathaniel-phillips#|archive-date=2018-08-06|dead-url=no|df=}}</ref> He missed a large part of the [[2017–18 Professional U23 Development League|2017–18 season]] due to a back injury. He captains the [[Liverpool F.C. Reserves and Academy#U23s|Liverpool U23]] squad, and was promoted to the first team squad for the [[2018–19 Liverpool F.C. season|2018–19 season]]. He is yet to play in a senior game.
